parcel.name: Angell XR at 43 Diamond Road
parcel.label: club
parcel.description:
# Collaborators Welcome!
This is a collaborative space for the Angell XR and Open Metaverse communities. Expect wearables, Indie art, events, and portals to other projects. 

Ideally this space can be used as a test bed for interoperability. To get involved visit angellxr.com or omigroup.com

collectible.name: Scarcity Tales: Water Faction
collectible.description: The mayor of Abundance, Tilt, only cared about the expansion of the Empire, and he was not in the island when Drog called the town meeting. Tilt was looking for the Atlantis with the army deep inside the ocean. The old legends told that Atlantis people had a marvelous treasure full of magic items; and gnomes love to transform magic in technology. The Water Faction was formed by Tiltâ€™s followers that were looking for magic in the depths of the ocean. But they were not a real faction until they returned and saw that Abundance had turned into Scarcity.
collectible.author: 0xe330dc28b47d73884ad88837aecfee1f49ad7e7b

collectible.name: Metaverse Verified in Voxels
collectible.description: A gift for NeonGlitch86 and EclecticMethod's Metaverse Verified holders made by GhostAgent and Bitpixi! Now you can apply this wearable above your head in Voxels. Does it grant you special privileges? No, not really.
